stimulusHtml: What is printed as a result of executing the code segment?

features.html:
Consider the following code segment.

 

if (false && true || false) 
{ 
   if (false || true && false) 
   { 
      System.out.print("First"); 
   } 
   else 
   { 
      System.out.print("Second"); 
   } 
} 
 
if (true || true && false) 
{ 
   System.out.print("Third"); 
}
